data.name: spigotcheck.ToolTip
data.value:
Spigot is a Bukkit equivalent that is still online.
Features: Clients do not need any mods or plugins in order for your server to function A massive Variety of Bukkit plugins (most are compatible with Spigot too)

data.name: forge.ToolTip
data.value:
Forge Server's are more difficult to use as they require the client and server's mods to be exactly the same in order to function.
Features: Mods can add new items etc.
Negatives: Requires Client to have identical setup as server Some mods may not be compatible with servers
